Dialogs.Dialog: Yeah. There's nothing else we can do here.
Ah, it was fun！ Now, shall we go home？
I see. Shall we go home now？
Hah... It's already this time？ I have to go home now, although I don't want to.
It's this time already？ Then let's go home.
Well, it's about time for us to go home, right？
Right. Rinko was also thinking that we should leave.
Right. Rinko was thinking the same thing.
Well, we've been to every place. Now, let's go home.
Right. If you say so ▲小早川＊▲...
Well, where do we go after this...？
We're together now and you are escorting Rinko... Can you make your girlfriend feel satisfied？
There are so many fun things around here. Hey, which one do you think Rinko would enjoy？
Well, after this, where will you take Rinko to？
What do we do now？ Rinko can go anywhere you want.
...Now, where do you want to go？
Now, what do we do？ If there's a place you want to go, let's go.
Where do we go now？ It's good if you choose a place that Rinko likes.
Um... Where shall we go next？ Rinko will leave it to the boyfriend to decide then...
Where will you take me next？ I can leave it to you, right？
Where shall we go next？ If it's somewhere fun, I'll be happy...
What shall we do next？ Rinko has no comment, so you can decide it.
What do we do next？ Any recommendation？
Which movie will be good for both of us to enjoy？ What do you think？
What shall we watch...？ Ah！ Don't ever think about a porn movie, okay！？
I won't！！ What I want to watch is...
Hey, hey. Guess what Rinko wants to watch...
(From the ones showing now... Which one is good？)
Hmm？ These are all that are on show now... Which one do you like？
Well, what shall we watch？ Any recommendation？
What shall we watch？ Ah, if there's something you want to watch, just tell Rinko.
(I should choose one that both of us can enjoy...)
What shall we watch？ You have any preference？
Is there any interesting movie on show...？
Say... Can we watch another one？
Of course. What shall we watch this time？
Since we're here, why don't we watch another one？
Hey. Rinko still wants to watch a movie with you.
Then shall we watch another one？
Ah, I want to watch that movie, too...
Then how about we watch another one？
Hey, don't you want to watch that one too？
Hey, hey. The other movie also looks interesting.
Right. Shall we watch that one too？
Okay, fine. Seems like you understand Rinko well.
Hmm？ That sounds fun. I can't wait.
Yes, yes. It's like you can read Rinko's mind.
...I don't really get it. Anyway, I'll go.
Lemme see, that's totally something Rinko isn't interested in, but...
Why don't we have lunch somewhere？ Rinko wants to have a delicious meal...
Okay, just leave it to me.
Why don't we go eat somewhere？ I'll let you decide the place！
Just don't complain after I decide, okay？
It's noon already. Rinko wants to have lunch.
Let's have something to eat then.
Aren't you hungry？ Should we go somewhere for lunch？
Yeah, I think that sounds good.
It's almost noon. Should we go somewhere to eat？
I'm so hungry... Let's go eat something, okay？
Um... How about some tea？ It's okay if you don't want some, though...
It's all right. Let's go have a drink.
Hey, let's have some tea. Even the cheap one would do for me now.
Let's look for a nice one.
Rinko wants to have some tea~
Let's take a break. How about having some tea, too？
How about we stop for a drink somewhere？ I'm a little tired.
Let's get a drink. I want to rest for a moment.
Umm... Let's have dinner before heading home, okay？ It's already this late, after all.
Why don't we go eat something？ We're already here, after all.
It's getting late. How about we have dinner？
Let's go have something to eat then.
For Rinko's family, this is about dinnertime. Do you feel hungry？
I feel so hungry... I still can tolerate it, but shall we get something to eat？
Yeah, you asked me at the right time.
I feel so hungry... I still can tolerate it, but shall we get something to eat？
We're here. Hey, let's up hurry inside.
Ah, it's still not too late...
Umm... Rinko still has some time to spend with you.
Hey, just a little longer, okay...？
Rinko can still play for a little while longer, you know.
Really？ Where shall we go, then？
Then why don't we hang out a little longer？ Another location's good.
Why don't we hang out a little longer？
Well then, why don't we go to another place？
I guess that sounds okay. Where do you want to go？
Ah, then let's hang out a little longer.
Yeah！ Hey, hey. Where will we go？
I think we shouldn't go home too late.
But, I guess it's time for us to go home.
Ah, we have to go home.
Okay, it's been decided. Let's hurry there.
If it's there... I don't think we have enough time.
We don't have enough time to go there.
Ah, if it's there, I guess we don't have enough time...
Ah, is that so？ What a pity.
It won't be good. Let's just stop.
...Eh？ There？ Umm... I don't want to.
You just don't understand a girl's feelings！ Stop！ Just stop！
Huh？ Well, if you say so...
